  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The agro-ecological production of vegetables in backyard gardens by Llano de las Flores families has been affected by lack of protection from sun and intense rains during some periods of the year. Families will be trained and provided with materials necessary to install structures with shade cloth in 20 backyard vegetable gardens in order to provide shade and protection during rainy season. Activities to be undertaken are: community assemblies for organization and establishing agreements; training workshop for improving vegetable gardens&apos; purchase and transport of material; day of community and family work for protecting the gardens</narrative>
